<HL>
   Diamond Sales Fell 6%
   In 1991, De Beers Says
   ----
   Special to The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
01/07/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   DBRSY
</CO>
